g.text: There are no hard-and-fast rules. Simply
as often as you can, wherever you have a chance, and
feel its positive, calming influence enter your mind and life
Hare Krishna Hare Krishna Krishna Krishna Hare Hare
Hare Rama Hare Rama Rama Rama Hare Hare
This Hare Krishna mantra is a sacred sound that can bring peace and
fearlessness even in times of turmoil.
